column5: Where can I pick this stuff up from around the Dunnville area? (I tried Partsource, Wal-Mart, Canadian Tire, and Princess Auto in the Hamilton area all without luck today).  I hear Napa sells the stuff. Can anyone confirm where it is definitely located?  Thanks!

I don't know where Dunnville is, sorry, but I got mine at Benson Auto Parts in Sturgeon Falls.  Here's a link for their store locations that might help:  http://www.autopartsextra.com/en/location_Ont.htm
Not sure about NAPA but I get it from Carquest, do a google search to find a store around Dunville
